-- Australia's Coalition Plans for 2012-13 Budgetary Surplus, Hockey Says
-- Marion Rae
-- 2010-07-28T21:28:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/australia-s-coalition-plans-for-2012-13-budgetary-surplus-hockey-says.html

          
          
             Australia’s opposition Liberal-
National coalition aims to deliver a budget surplus “at least”
as soon as the incumbent Labor government has promised in
2012-13 and can’t pledge cuts in personal income tax rates,
Opposition Treasury spokesman Joe Hockey told Australian
Broadcasting Corp. radio today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
